sentence: list the nonstop flights from miami to new york on a sunday along with the fares that are less than four hundred sixty six dollars
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v2.fare_id||'"',
 v0.stops, '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.airport_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.city_name||'"', '"'||v7.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.day_name||'"', '"'||v1.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.fare_id||'"',
 v2.one_direction_cost, '"'||v8.fare_basis_code||'"',
 '"'||v9.days_code||'"', '"'||v9.day_name||'"' FROM flight v0,
 flight_fare v1, fare v2, airport_service v3, city v4,
 airport_service v5, city v6, days v7, fare_basis v8, days v9 
WHERE (((((v0.stops =  0) AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) AND (v4.city_name = 'MIAMI'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) 
AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) AND (v6.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) 
AND ((v0.flight_days = ANY v7.days_code) 
AND (v7.day_name = 'SUNDAY'))))) AND (v0.flight_id = v1.flight_id)) 
AND (v1.fare_id = v2.fare_id)) AND ((v2.one_direction_cost <  466) 
AND ((v2.fare_basis_code = ANY v8.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v8.basis_days = ANY v9.days_code) AND (v9.day_name = 'SUNDAY')))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID , FARE.FARE_ID FROM FLIGHT , FLIGHT_FARE , FARE WHERE ( FLIGHT.STOPS = 0 AND ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MIAMI ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' NEW YORK ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' SUNDAY ' ) ) ) ) AND FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID = FLIGHT_FARE.FLIGHT_ID AND FLIGHT_FARE.FARE_ID = FARE.FARE_ID AND ( FARE.ONE_DIRECTION_COST < 466 AND FARE . FARE_BASIS_CODE IN ( SELECT FARE_BASIS . FARE_BASIS_CODE FROM FARE_BASIS WHERE FARE_BASIS . BASIS_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' SUNDAY ' ) ) ) ) ;
